1
00:01:08,319 --> 00:01:09,760
This is the 23rd draft I've written.

2
00:01:09,959 --> 00:01:11,120
I'm quite confident in it.

3
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:15,359
The country is at peace,

4
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,599
and the people are happy.

5
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,879
General Yan Ying

6
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:22,120
and Prince Xiao Chengjing

7
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:24,319
are getting married.

8
00:01:25,799 --> 00:01:28,280
Pearls and embroidered curtains,

9
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:31,519
they are getting married.

10
00:01:32,719 --> 00:01:35,640
Suddenly, an old woman came in to stop them.

11
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,319
No!

12
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,959
You two are siblings?

13
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:44,000
Siblings?

14
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,719
Look back first.

15
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,000
It's more exciting.

16
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:49,719
Yan Ying was shocked.

17
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:50,719
She ran out of the tent

18
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:52,400
like crazy.

19
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,079
No.

20
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,079
At this time,

21
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:58,200
she bumped into a man.

22
00:01:59,359 --> 00:02:00,519
Love at first sight.

23
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,920
Love at first sight.

24
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,040
When they passed by,

25
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,840
[He's in a white robe.]

26
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,359
[His skin is like fresh milk.]

27
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,599
[He's a gentleman.]

28
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:09,879
[He's as gentle as jade.]

29
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,159
[He held Yan Ying with his long]

30
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,280
[and tender hands.]

31
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,960
[The man said in a low voice,]

32
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,680
["Be careful, Miss."]

33
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,599
[Yan Ying didn't take her eyes off him]

34
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:25,719
[and said absent-mindedly,]

35
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:26,840
["It seems that]

36
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,000
[we've met somewhere before."]

37
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:32,120
[The man smiled and replied,]

38
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,719
I'm Long Aotian.

39
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:36,240
Hmm.

40
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:37,400
What...

41
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:39,439
What...

42
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,400
What is this Long Aotian?

43
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:43,280
Yan Ying's lost love.

44
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,560
I added a prequel.

45
00:02:45,319 --> 00:02:47,919
They met in the world

46
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,599
and forgot each other in the world.

47
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,280
Years have passed.

48
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:54,000
Every time I wake up at midnight,

49
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,639
I'm haunted by her.

50
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,639
Fine.

51
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,080
It's a dual male lead story?

52
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,159
Of course.

53
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,759
The perfect guy

54
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,000
and the charming guy.

55
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,719
A beautiful love story.

56
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,879
It's so touching.

57
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,719
So,

58
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:12,360
is this the ending you wanted?

59
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,439
Blue didn't say that.

60
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,840
She said if you want to submit it,

61
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:20,360
you must understand market concepts,

62
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:21,439
product thinking,

63
00:03:22,319 --> 00:03:24,639
and the characters must be distinctive.

64
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:26,120
The emotions must be intense.

65
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,560
The plot must be melodramatic.

66
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,400
But

67
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:31,680
this is not the ending I want.

68
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,439
I've never been

69
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,439
so confused in my life.

70
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,000
I'll change it.

71
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:46,159
It's not whether you change it or not.

72
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:48,800
It's whether it works or not.

73
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:51,719
Then

74
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,360
how can I know

75
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,560
whether it works or not?

76
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:05,919
I got it.

77
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,319
Come with me.

78
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:20,720
So,

79
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:24,000
the way to verify whether the rewriting is successful is

80
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,279
to eat spicy food?

81
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:26,439
Exactly.

82
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,439
I never ate spicy food before.

83
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:29,959
This time,

84
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:32,319
I specifically added the feature of not fearing spicy food to myself.

85
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,800
If the rewriting is successful,

86
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:36,240
it means

87
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,519
I can continue rewriting.

88
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,079
Alright.

89
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:01,480
I ate so much and there's no reaction.

90
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,240
It means it didn't work.

91
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:03,959
No.

92
00:05:04,439 --> 00:05:05,879
Maybe it's not time yet.

93
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:06,879
I'll try again.

94
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:19,920
Have some water.

95
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,879
Every novel

96
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,639
is a new universe.

97
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,240
If you want to rewrite the ending,

98
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,079
you have to let the original author

99
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:31,920
make the changes on the original account.

100
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,160
Ah.

101
00:05:39,759 --> 00:05:40,639
My good brother.

102
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,160
Come on.

103
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,279
This can relieve the spiciness.

104
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,040
Thank you.

105
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:53,920
What are you doing here?

106
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,399
Why can't I come if I'm free?

107
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,319
Hello, I'm Xu Mengxi.

108
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,959
Xu Mengxi?

109
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,079
Yes.

110
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:08,399
You are really Xu Mengxi?

111
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,759
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

112
00:06:11,279 --> 00:06:12,680
I just met him today too.

113
00:06:12,879 --> 00:06:15,000
Miss Yan, is there anything you need?

114
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,160
I'm Xu Chi's brother.

115
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,199
Since you are Xu Chi's friend,

116
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:20,079
I will definitely

117
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,439
help you with your business.

118
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,560
Okay.

119
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,439
Not everyone in this world can be like me.

120
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,959
Not everyone can accept your identity so easily.

121
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:28,839
Calm down.

122
00:06:31,959 --> 00:06:32,480
Oh.

123
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,879
Mr. Wei'an,

124
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:42,199
I really like the novel Galaxy War you wrote.

125
00:06:43,399 --> 00:06:45,000
It's very important

126
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,000
to me.

127
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:48,800
Oh.

128
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:52,680
So you're a fan of Galaxy Chronicles?

129
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:54,839
Yes.

130
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:58,560
But it's been years since I wrote it.

131
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,720
I've forgotten

132
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,879
what I wrote back then.

133
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,959
And I don't want

134
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:06,199
to hear the name Wei'an again.

135
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:07,839
No.

136
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,399
Maybe you don't care,

137
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,279
but for some people,

138
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,639
that name

139
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:16,079
means a lot.

140
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:18,480
Xu Chi reacted so strongly

141
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,959
when she mentioned the name Weian.

142
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:21,600
Maybe she can be the breakthrough

143
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,360
for Xu Chi to get over the shadow of Weian.

144
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:25,120
Actually, I have a few more questions

145
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,959
about Galaxy Chronicle.

146
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,319
It's late.

147
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,399
There's a meeting later.

148
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,199
Let's go.

149
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:33,279
Didn't the meeting end today?

150
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:34,279
There's an additional one.

151
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:35,560
What?

152
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,759
You can go if you have something to do.

153
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:38,879
I'll pay the bill.

154
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,079
Sorry, Mr. Wei'an.

155
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:42,319
Oh, right.

156
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,480
Miss Yan.

157
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,920
There will be a book exchange party this weekend.

158
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:49,720
Would you like to come?

159
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,360
Okay.

160
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:50,680
No.

161
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,519
I will definitely go.

162
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,639
Okay, see you this weekend.

163
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:54,319
Okay.

164
00:07:54,319 --> 00:07:54,839
Bye.

165
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,680
I will definitely go.

166
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,920
Waiter, please give me a pair of bowls and chopsticks.

167
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,600
Okay.
